Comment: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看起來已經修改好了就是...
Comment: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是怎麼了
Comment: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明好像很高興 眼淚卻流出來了
Comment: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底怎麼了
Comment: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,恭喜妳了
Comment: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要好好的辦場出道慶功宴呢
Comment: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼...我有個願望
Comment: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼?
Comment: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,唸我的名字
Comment: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,椎名?
Comment: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是那個
Comment: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊...喂...那個還真的是沒辦法...
Comment: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒唸過女孩的名字過...
Comment: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是你就叫美咲了
Comment: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是外星人!!
Comment: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,千尋也是
Comment: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是女強人!!
Comment: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼 我是?
Comment: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那...那個...
Comment: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不公平
Comment: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真白
Comment: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,果然...
Comment: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,果然什麼啊?
Comment: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說不出口
Comment: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼啊 那...
Comment: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,青澀啊 真是青澀啊 空太
Comment: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,青春啊...心跳撲通撲通
Comment: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,姐姐我都流汗了呢
Comment: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等...等等 從哪裡開始聽到的啊!!
Comment: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂!我有希望讓你知道的事
Comment: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從一開始...
Comment: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,呀啊~~什麼什麼 說出來說出來
Comment: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你也有想讓我們知道的事不是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好了好了~不要害羞
Comment: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把想說的話盡量都丟出來
Comment: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,造成大家的困擾 非常對不起
Comment: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請讓我再一次 留在櫻花莊!!
Comment: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,恭喜真白出道!!
Comment: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還有 後輩 歡迎回來!
Comment: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,非常謝謝
Comment: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不客氣
Comment: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把沒發生的事推卸到某人的身上
Comment: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 並不是這樣
Comment: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要有那份心 世界會有一瞬間改變色彩
Comment: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,櫻花莊有著許多顏色混雜在一起非常混亂
Comment: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:42.88,Default,effect 06,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:44.12,effect 06,effect07,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:43.21,effect 06,,0,0,0,,06
Comment: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是...在這將來 永遠不會變的事
Comment: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喵~
Comment: 0,0:23:42.36,0:23:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,title,
Comment: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,小光是母的
Comment: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喵~喵~
Comment: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有雌性要增加了的預感
Comment: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,小光這樣講

