Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}接下來是關東地區的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}由於低氣壓將從西邊進來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到了夜晚可能會降雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就這些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼要搬出櫻花莊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:28.33,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為只要待在櫻花莊 我會變得討厭自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:30.48,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}討厭?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.88,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以我要離開櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一開始就那麼打算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}新人獎的截止日期快到了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會為妳加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在離開櫻花莊之前 我會繼續照顧妳的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不用為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:57.76,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名 好像每天徹夜工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}畫了又改 畫了又改一直重複著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}新人獎截止日當天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}終於把原稿完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:25.02,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}尋找貓咪飼主的事情只剩下小光和小望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}今晚很可惜沒辦法看到銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就這樣 想搬去一般宿舍的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之先告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:40.89,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後輩 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:47.43,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了...這穿著...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:52.28,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有那樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5} 後輩超討厭的啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:01:58.39,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.25,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:05.60,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好可愛 快受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想玩玩看壞哥哥監禁play之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她們是想讓你說這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.58,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}裡面摻雜著性騷擾發言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:20.51,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}美咲說要慶祝七夕 所以連你的份都準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:09.82,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總覺得...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.34,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小鬼太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:17.10,Default,千尋,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}上井草特別受小朋友歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為精神年齡比較相近呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.97,Default,小朋友,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大姐姐 我也要掛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.92,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}哦  姐姐抱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:24.88,Default,小朋友,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再高一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.22,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好 再高一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:26.96,Default,小朋友,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再高一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.64,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要是碰到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你過的不會是銀河而是奈何橋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.37,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}仁也寫點嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.37,Default,小朋友,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要掛在那邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.09,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那走囉!走囉!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.78,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即使沒有名字也知道是誰寫的啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:48.45,Default,小朋友,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再高點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.50,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經不是七夕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是的 是小學生嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.06,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.41,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不知道要寫些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:12.29,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都那麼努力了 就許願得新人獎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.02,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.60,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:18.39,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要自己爭取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.68,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳還真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.18,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼很厲害?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.03,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不 總覺得閃耀著光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.04,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒看見星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.86,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也是 看不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為還是陰天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.36,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}掛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也要掛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.06,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}掛吧掛吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:05.24,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}早知道剛剛就在上面寫希望不會下雨就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.44,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然送不出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.84,Default,千尋,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣一來牛郎就無法見到織女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可喜可賀 可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:20.88,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}待會要好好洗澡喔 不然會感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:33.42,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真白 她沒戴那條項鍊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:39.52,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 那應該說是約會...還是誤會呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:43.72,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.05,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:51.47,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}新人獎選拔落選了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.96,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒關係 下次一定會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.92,Default-UP,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我到底再說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒必要拘泥在新人獎 而且不是有編輯人了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.40,Default-UP,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想說的明明不是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經和其他人等級不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以新人獎落榜也沒必要在意...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.51,Default,真白,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要回房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:27.84,Default,美咲,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小真白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後輩 !?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等一下 後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}仁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.09,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.60,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼最差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}美咲的動畫新作你看了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.66,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}動畫新作是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在椎名歡迎會上放的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.06,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不止大受好評
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}公開3天內就有100萬點閱數
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是5分鐘的動畫 就來了10封表示想商業化的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.94,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家都很期待 美咲的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就只有我希望她這次會失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次能被批評得一無是處 我是真的這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.74,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總覺得鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我稍微鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽到椎名落選
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:09:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名明明拼命地努力 為了新人獎那麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.62,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我明明都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.08,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才能這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會在不知不覺中把周圍的人捲進去並使其傷痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}越接近的人 越容易被摧殘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在凡人無法抵達的高處 有這麼一群人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:27.74,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們怎麼也看不到的 在雲上的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們就在那樣的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:41.93,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不覺得美咲學姊會去在意才能或實力什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.66,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是啊 我完全不知道要如何接受和美咲之間的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:55.60,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在能堂堂正正地站在她身旁之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我只能繼續當花花公子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.42,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}仁 該不會對美咲學姊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.74,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吃點拉麵什麼的再回去吧 我請客喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:14.66,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在才擔心雖然有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.72,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒什麼不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不論哪邊都是真實的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}代表自己並沒那麼單純
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.66,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:49.64,Default,空太,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明一直宅在房裡 卻知道不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:16.02,Default,女僕,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要說遍體鱗傷這台詞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就在遍體鱗傷之前把那些書讀完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.96,Default,仁,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}比起金八 仙八更合我意的女僕敬上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}早飯...我放在這裡囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}唉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒人要整理這些東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我如果不在之後 打算怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}空太的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.82,Default-UP,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}常常說強顏歡笑什麼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.06,Default-UP,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}其實把悲傷的思念都埋藏在心裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的願望什麼的 是怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼 今天就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}神田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我放學後的打工翹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:13:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛好休假 一起去找願意領養貓飼主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總是麻煩妳啊 青山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}終於快到小希和小光的離去時候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}神田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣真的好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳是指什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為 總覺得看著神田同學 我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能稍微占用一點時間嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}神田同學...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那...那個 找我有事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為很喜歡甜的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喔...這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喜歡甜的東西和鹹的東西混在一起的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這...這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很失落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個...讀看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}油菜花莊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名在畫的方面很完美 缺點只有故事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}既然如此 我叫她想像一下實際在櫻花莊發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我和椎名的立場相反了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別多說 繼續看下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒辦法決定自己該穿什麼內褲的少年其實有著明確的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}另一方面找不到該做什麼的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有個更嚴重問題就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就如你所見並無HAPPY END  有頭沒尾的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這就是椎名落選最大的原因喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從油菜花莊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可是苦苦勸說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}最後結局要再重新想一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那孩子沒聽進我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說那是....空太的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真好~真好~有疾走感的青春結局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我起雞皮疙瘩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說不定會有什麼辦法也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的願望...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}千尋老師!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊勒~怎麼了 神田 有東西沒拿?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}首先 從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼就先這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的願望...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名覺得那樣就好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再更誠實點 寫出自己的期望結局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的...期望結局...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯 妳的期望結局是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的願望...才不是希望從櫻花莊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}擅自給自己壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只想要從櫻花莊 從現實逃離而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的願望...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣子就好 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...有希望讓妳知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...交出志願調查表了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}進入媒體學系 並打算製作遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:43.58,Default-UP,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我回來啦~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}願望是想挑戰看看製作企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想成為遊戲製作家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然從之前就有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}事先想了無法成功的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}浪費時間之類的 不想受傷之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}滿是無法去做的理由排在一起 放棄自己踏出往前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...看著椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想要改變自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...總有一天也要像妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又...熬夜畫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然...我還是想待在油菜花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這就是...椎名的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真正的HAPPY END?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼在這種地方....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}接起來 空太接起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊 是 這是椎名的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}咦...啊 剛才很謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}起床了 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出道...決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}空太嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}笨蛋 是妳的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然沒有獲得新人獎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那份原稿修改之後 下個月後可以刊載出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看起來已經修改好了就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明好像很高興 眼淚卻流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}恭喜妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要好好的辦場出道慶功宴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼...我有個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}唸我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}椎名?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊...喂...那個還真的是沒辦法...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒唸過女孩的名字過...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是你就叫美咲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那是外星人!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}千尋也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那是女強人!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼 我是?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼啊 那...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}青澀啊 真是青澀啊 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}青春啊...心跳撲通撲通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}姐姐我都流汗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等...等等 從哪裡開始聽到的啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!我有希望讓你知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從一開始...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}呀啊~~什麼什麼 說出來說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你也有想讓我們知道的事不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好了好了~不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把想說的話盡量都丟出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}造成大家的困擾 非常對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請讓我再一次 留在櫻花莊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}恭喜真白出道!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還有 後輩 歡迎回來!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}非常謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把沒發生的事推卸到某人的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要有那份心 世界會有一瞬間改變色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}櫻花莊有著許多顏色混雜在一起非常混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那是...在這將來 永遠不會變的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小光是母的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喵~喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有雌性要增加了的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小光這樣講
